title: 2019 Week 11 Preview
itunes:title: 2019 Week 11 Preview
description:
A room filled with heroes- Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler, Chris Wesseling, and Gregg Rosenthal preview every game for week 11 with their game picking draft style. The heroes reflect on some of their favorite matchups of the upcoming week like Ravens Texans (6:00) and the super bowl rematch between the Patriots and Eagles (13:00).

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
